  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to compare the efficacy of transdermal fentanyl to placebo
      both administered together with peroral nonsteroidal antiinflammatory drug (NSAID) and
      paracetamol in treatment of postoperative pain after hallux valgus or hallux rigidus
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
